    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a masterclass in automotive preservation. This unit features a blueprint-perfect powertrain with zero drivetrain lash and a forced induction system that maintains rock-solid boost pressure across the entire power band. The suspension geometry has been kept in factory-spec alignment, ensuring razor-sharp turn-in and exceptional lateral stability. Every fluid change has been documented to ensure peak thermal management and internal component longevity. This isn't just a car; it's a turn-key specimen with a crisp throttle response and a linear torque curve that must be experienced to be believed. Mechanically flawless and aesthetically peerless.",
